    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>试玩内容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎，骑士们！《Lonely Mountains: Snow Riders》试玩版邀请你在Solo模式下或在线竞速模式中与最多8名骑士一起征服孤山“坦嫩斯泰因”上的前两个雪道。Zen模式和团队模式在试玩中被锁定，且只有一种滑雪类型可用。进度和自定义项目限制在10级，已调整为在较短时间内提供更多变化。快速匹配只包含两个雪道。排行榜功能可用。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于主游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/c1e9ee0bc04d0c14c6ff5a82d86a8a34.poster.avif?t=1766071928\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/c1e9ee0bc04d0c14c6ff5a82d86a8a34.webm?t=1766071928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/c1e9ee0bc04d0c14c6ff5a82d86a8a34.mp4?t=1766071928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>深呼吸，倒数三个数，然后……出发！《Lonely Mountains: Snow Riders》是一款滑雪速降游戏。您可以穿越皑皑雪山，滑过冰湖，来一个炫酷的跳跃，飞越令人惊叹的美景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/c2e8d574a664324c6ba4828df96e3000.avif?t=1766071928\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/ad2f5adcfdf014869caa65145e4a1dd3.poster.avif?t=1766071928\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/ad2f5adcfdf014869caa65145e4a1dd3.webm?t=1766071928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/ad2f5adcfdf014869caa65145e4a1dd3.mp4?t=1766071928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lonely Mountains 系列的新作《Snow Riders》带来了全新功能——在线多人游戏！在合作模式下，和小队成员一起征服雪山，且途中可添加存档点；或是在对战模式中比拼速度。支持 2-8 名玩家同时游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/0e75ae13eab2bf6e1fd88e1a302bcae6.avif?t=1766071928\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/bd3e2b4450bcf84fd7224e8ae6d72a02.poster.avif?t=1766071928\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/bd3e2b4450bcf84fd7224e8ae6d72a02.webm?t=1766071928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/bd3e2b4450bcf84fd7224e8ae6d72a02.mp4?t=1766071928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尝试令人胆战心惊的技巧，或是刷新最快时间，登上排行榜。当然，您也可以选择人迹罕至的道路，在探索雪道时寻找捷径，不断解锁新装备、服装和技巧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是寻找刺激的挑战，还是与朋友一起度过轻松的假期，《Lonely Mountains: Snow Riders》都将是您的完美冬季度假胜地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/d9e8171004517f249ca385d11ba149d3.poster.avif?t=1766071928\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/d9e8171004517f249ca385d11ba149d3.webm?t=1766071928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238120/extras/d9e8171004517f249ca385d11ba149d3.mp4?t=1766071928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
